With the Service added in the Program.cs file, I should be able to DI the service into the Razor page and called the methods of the interface which is an API call.

### Steps To Reproduce

Create a new Blazor Web Application. Add a interface and class file, add the interface to the program as a Singleton. Inject the interface into a razor page. Call a method in a OnInitializedAsync.

